<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <style>
        .privacy-header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
           
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .privacy-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .privacy-container {
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .privacy-content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-content h2 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .privacy-content p,
        .privacy-content ul {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .privacy-content ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar bg-dark " style="  font-family:  Georgia,Times New Roman, Times, serif" ;></nav>
    <div class=" mt-3 container-fluid border-bottom border-white privacy-heade privacy-header">

        <a href="/"> <img src="./logo2.png" alt="logo" width="120" height="100"
                class="navbar-brand img-thumbnail border-0  mb-3" style="cursor: pointer;background-color:white;"></a>

        <div class="text-center">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </nav>



    <!-- Privacy Content -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="privacy-container">
            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This privacy
                    policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our blog.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your name</li>
                    <li>Email address</li>
                    <li>Content of comments or messages</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use your information to improve our blog, provide personalized content, and communicate with you.
                    We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as required by law.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. Contact us at <a
                        href="mailto:sblogify@gmail.com" class="footer-link">sblogify@gmail.com</a> to exercise these
                    rights.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The updated policy will be posted on this page
                    with the "Last updated" date.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer class="text-center py-4">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Blogify. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="/contact_us" class="footer-link">Contact Us</a></p>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script></script>
</body>

</html>